<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Sketchboard</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./stylesheets/sketch.css" />
    <script src="./javascripts/jquery-1.11.2.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.socket.io/socket.io-1.2.0.js"></script>
    <script src="./javascripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./javascripts/main.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <section onmousedown="return false" class="menu">
        <h1>Sketch Board</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-cus" id="drawCircle">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-cus" id="drawSquare">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-stop" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-cus" id="drawTriangle">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
        <br>
        <p>더블클릭으로 도형 편집을 활성/비활성화 할 수 있습니다.</p>
        <p>방향키로 활성화된 도형을 이동시킬 수 있습니다.</p>
        <p>delete키를 통해 활성화된 도형을 제거할 수 있습니다.</p>
        <p>esc키를 통해 활성화된 도형을 모두 비활성화 시킬 수 있습니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="board">

    </section>


    <script>
        document.ondblclick = function(evt) {
            if (window.getSelection)
                window.getSelection().removeAllRanges();
            else if (document.selection)
                document.selection.empty();
        }

        // var socket = io();
        var sketch = new Sketch();
    </script>
</body>
</html>